{"tid":1291053,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(文宣)搞個比藍絲更藍嘅Facebook page 整唔整得過？","createTime":"2019-07-06T17:09:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-06T17:14:41.000Z","uid":55770,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0fa95b00f4660bfbd6b5d0fff28e08f28dd6bc27","tid":1291053,"uid":55770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T17:09:20.000Z","msg":"早前比藍絲更藍 比黨更紅嘅策略真係好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但奈何我屋企嘅爹娘已經知道我嘅立場<br />\n 就算我講乜都唔入耳<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n再扮藍絲只會令佢加深警剔<br />\n<br />\n另外都有諗過幫佢like下蘋果 立場<br />\n但呢啲都太出名 佢一睇個名已經睇唔落啲內容<br />\n<br />\n如果搵巴絲整個比藍絲更藍嘅Facebook page點睇？定已經有？有冇人可以推薦下？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/03.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db80a68579e29cec6fc445a18644eece61d96e18","tid":1291053,"uid":200758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T17:10:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7twnFnB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7twnFnB.jpg&h=df2571ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T3Kkr2C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT3Kkr2C.jpg&h=b6c70bc2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mTXidHD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmTXidHD.jpg&h=a6d55b00&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cc51c6741cbbbe7e610abcceb10bcc9b6f149cc0","tid":1291053,"uid":55770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T17:11:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78b2ad548ca83f208144344e2459c97b34c56ff9","tid":1291053,"uid":55770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T17:11:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b00bf6e81e9c36d730bd0a57471f1cb66fa4abf3","tid":1291053,"uid":55770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cited